relevant_findings.HEENT: PERRL, EOMI. No scleral icterus. Bilateral mild conjunctival injection. Mucous membranes moist. No oral ulcers.
relevant_findings.lungs: CTA bilaterally, no wheezes, rales, rhonchi. Normal respiratory effort.

relevant_findings.extremities: Warm and well perfused, no cyanosis, clubbing, edema.
